Package org.bukkit.inventory.meta.trim

Interface TrimPattern

All Superinterfaces:
net.kyori.adventure.key.Keyed, Keyed
@MinecraftExperimental @Experimental public interface TrimPattern extends Keyed
Represents a pattern that may be used in an ArmorTrim.
API Note:
Armor trims are part of an experimental feature of Minecraft and hence subject to change. Constants in this class may be null if a data pack is not present to enable these features.
